            <title><![CDATA[【[干饭人]#吃素或不吃主食减肥靠谱吗#】春节假期后，大家胖了多少斤？[磕到了]通过吃素或不吃主食的方法来减肥，靠谱吗？专家提示，#适量吃主食不会发胖#。长期...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[干饭人]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/cb/2022_Foodie_org.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%90%83%E7%B4%A0%E6%88%96%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%83%E4%B8%BB%E9%A3%9F%E5%87%8F%E8%82%A5%E9%9D%A0%E8%B0%B1%E5%90%97%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%90%83%E7%B4%A0%E6%88%96%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%83%E4%B8%BB%E9%A3%9F%E5%87%8F%E8%82%A5%E9%9D%A0%E8%B0%B1%E5%90%97%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#吃素或不吃主食减肥靠谱吗#</span></a>】春节假期后，大家胖了多少斤？[磕到了]通过吃素或不吃主食的方法来减肥，靠谱吗？专家提示，<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E9%80%82%E9%87%8F%E5%90%83%E4%B8%BB%E9%A3%9F%E4%B8%8D%E4%BC%9A%E5%8F%91%E8%83%96%23&amp;extparam=%23%E9%80%82%E9%87%8F%E5%90%83%E4%B8%BB%E9%A3%9F%E4%B8%8D%E4%BC%9A%E5%8F%91%E8%83%96%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#适量吃主食不会发胖#</span></a>。长期不吃或少吃碳水化合物容易引发低血糖、肠道功能异常、记忆力下降等症状；而不吃肉容易出现缺铁性贫血、肌肉衰减、骨质疏松、记忆力衰退等症状。<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>阿卫提醒，管住嘴迈开腿才是减肥的关键<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[许愿星]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/a8/2022_WishingStar_org.png" data-rsshub-image="href" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（央视网）<a href="http://t.cn/A6YoHA8d" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a>]]></description>
